<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Unicode on 随记</title><link>/tags/unicode/</link><description>Recent content in Unicode on 随记</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>zh-cn</language><lastBuildDate>Tue, 15 Jul 2025 22:00:00 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="/tags/unicode/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>支持大字符集的中文字体</title><link>/posts/free-chinese-unicode-fonts/</link><pubDate>Tue, 15 Jul 2025 22:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>/posts/free-chinese-unicode-fonts/</guid><description>&lt;p>除了 Mi Sans，其它字体的覆盖汉字数量只是预估。 黑体推荐阿里巴巴普惠体 3.0、Mi Sans + Mi Sans L3、Vivo Sans 和遍黑(Plangothic)，可以商用；宋体有天珩全字库、超集宋体，开心宋体，楷体只有天珩，注意这些都不能商用（2025 更新：&lt;a href="https://github.com/takushun-wu/WenJinMincho/blob/main/INTRODUCE.md">文津宋体&lt;/a>覆盖 Unicode 16.0，可以商用）。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Unicode 中的点符号</title><link>/posts/dots-in-unicode/</link><pubDate>Sat, 15 Mar 2025 22:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>/posts/dots-in-unicode/</guid><description>&lt;table>
 &lt;thead>
 &lt;tr>
 &lt;th style="text-align: center">字符&lt;/th>
 &lt;th style="text-align: left">名字&lt;/th>
 &lt;th style="text-align: center">编码&lt;/th>
 &lt;th>区块&lt;/th>
 &lt;th>解释&lt;/th>
 &lt;/tr>
 &lt;/thead>
 &lt;tbody>
 &lt;tr>
 &lt;td style="text-align: center">&lt;strong>.&lt;/strong>&lt;/td>
 &lt;td style="text-align: left">DOT 或 FULL STOP&lt;/td>
 &lt;td style="text-align: center">002E&lt;/td>
 &lt;td>Basic Latin&lt;/td>
 &lt;td>ASCII 的点，句号，键盘直接输入&lt;/td>
 &lt;/tr>
 &lt;tr>
 &lt;td style="text-align: center">&lt;strong>·&lt;/strong>&lt;/td>
 &lt;td style="text-align: left">&lt;mark>MIDDLE DOT&lt;/mark>&lt;/td>
 &lt;td style="text-align: center">00B7&lt;/td>
 &lt;td>Latin-1 Supplement&lt;/td>
 &lt;td>中国大陆《&lt;a href="http://www.sac.gov.cn/SACSearch/search?channelid=160591&amp;amp;templet=gjcxjg_detail.jsp&amp;amp;searchword=STANDARD_CODE=%27GB/T%2015834-2011%27&amp;amp;XZ=T">标点符号用法&lt;/a>》（GB/T 15834-2011）规定的中文间隔号，星陈输入法： &lt;br/>/bdjg&lt;br/>/bdjgh&lt;br/>/jg&lt;br/>/jgh&lt;br/>bdjg&lt;br/>kkjg&lt;/td>
 &lt;/tr>
 &lt;tr>
 &lt;td style="text-align: center">&lt;strong>•&lt;/strong>&lt;/td>
 &lt;td style="text-align: left">BULLET&lt;/td>
 &lt;td style="text-align: center">2022&lt;/td>
 &lt;td>General Punctuation&lt;/td>
 &lt;td>列表中的项目&lt;/td>
 &lt;/tr>
 &lt;tr>
 &lt;td style="text-align: center">&lt;strong>‧&lt;/strong>&lt;/td>
 &lt;td style="text-align: left">&lt;u>HYPHENATION POINT&lt;/u>&lt;/td>
 &lt;td style="text-align: center">2027&lt;/td>
 &lt;td>General Punctuation&lt;/td>
 &lt;td>在西文字典中，表示单词中音节的分隔位置，例如 dic‧tion‧ar‧ies。根据台湾“教育部”《重订标点符号手册》，历史上是把音界号做为间隔号使用。&lt;/td>
 &lt;/tr>
 &lt;tr>
 &lt;td style="text-align: center">&lt;strong>⋅&lt;/strong>&lt;/td>
 &lt;td style="text-align: left">DOT OPERATOR&lt;/td>
 &lt;td style="text-align: center">22C5&lt;/td>
 &lt;td>Mathematical Operators&lt;/td>
 &lt;td>数学符号&lt;/td>
 &lt;/tr>
 &lt;tr>
 &lt;td style="text-align: center">&lt;strong>⸱&lt;/strong>&lt;/td>
 &lt;td style="text-align: left">WORD SEPARATOR MIDDLE DOT&lt;/td>
 &lt;td style="text-align: center">2E31&lt;/td>
 &lt;td>Supplemental Punctuation&lt;/td>
 &lt;td>用于 Avestan，Carian，Georgian，Old Hungarian，Kaithi，Lydian，Samaritan。&lt;/td>
 &lt;/tr>
 &lt;tr>
 &lt;td style="text-align: center">&lt;strong>・&lt;/strong>&lt;/td>
 &lt;td style="text-align: left">&lt;mark>KATAKANA MIDDLE DOT&lt;/mark>&lt;/td>
 &lt;td style="text-align: center">30FB&lt;/td>
 &lt;td>Katakana&lt;/td>
 &lt;td>日语片假名的全角中点，星陈输入法：&lt;br/>/jmzd&lt;br/>/ryzd&lt;br/>/zd&lt;br/>jmzd&lt;br/>kkzd&lt;br/>ryzd&lt;/td>
 &lt;/tr>
 &lt;tr>
 &lt;td style="text-align: center">&lt;strong>ꞏ&lt;/strong>&lt;/td>
 &lt;td style="text-align: left">SINOLOGICAL DOT, LATIN LETTER&lt;/td>
 &lt;td style="text-align: center">A78F&lt;/td>
 &lt;td>Latin Extended-D&lt;/td>
 &lt;td>不常用，用于汉学研究的转写&lt;/td>
 &lt;/tr>
 &lt;tr>
 &lt;td style="text-align: center">&lt;strong>．&lt;/strong>&lt;/td>
 &lt;td style="text-align: left">FULLWIDTH FULL STOP&lt;/td>
 &lt;td style="text-align: center">FF0E&lt;/td>
 &lt;td>Halfwidth and Fullwidth Forms&lt;/td>
 &lt;td>中文全角句号，不推荐使用，星陈输入法：&lt;br/>/jh&lt;br/>kkjh&lt;/td>
 &lt;/tr>
 &lt;tr>
 &lt;td style="text-align: center">&lt;strong>･&lt;/strong>&lt;/td>
 &lt;td style="text-align: left">HALFWIDTH KATAKANA MIDDLE DOT&lt;/td>
 &lt;td style="text-align: center">FF65&lt;/td>
 &lt;td>Halfwidth and Fullwidth Forms&lt;/td>
 &lt;td>窄版的 U+30FB&lt;/td>
 &lt;/tr>
 &lt;tr>
 &lt;td style="text-align: center">&lt;strong>𐄁&lt;/strong>&lt;/td>
 &lt;td style="text-align: left">AEGEAN WORD SEPARATOR DOT&lt;/td>
 &lt;td style="text-align: center">10101&lt;/td>
 &lt;td>Aegean Numbers&lt;/td>
 &lt;td>爱琴海数字的分割点&lt;/td>
 &lt;/tr>
 &lt;/tbody>
&lt;/table>
&lt;p>参考：&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Perl Unicode 脚本模版</title><link>/posts/perl-unicode-script-template/</link><pubDate>Sat, 30 Mar 2024 12:26:39 +0800</pubDate><guid>/posts/perl-unicode-script-template/</guid><description>&lt;p>参考 &lt;a href="https://perldoc.perl.org/perl#Reference-Manual">perldoc perl&lt;/a> 里的以 perluni 开头的文档，至少用 Perl v5.36。&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="background-color:#f0f0f0;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-perl" data-lang="perl">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#60a0b0;font-style:italic">#!/usr/bin/env perl&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#60a0b0;font-style:italic"># https://perldoc.perl.org/perluniintro#Perl&amp;#39;s-Unicode-Support v5.28&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#60a0b0;font-style:italic"># https://perldoc.perl.org/feature#The-&amp;#39;signatures&amp;#39;-feature v5.36&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#60a0b0;font-style:italic"># https://perldoc.perl.org/perlunicook#℞-0:-Standard-preamble v5.36&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#007020;font-weight:bold">use&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#0e84b5;font-weight:bold">v5&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#40a070">.36&lt;/span>; &lt;span style="color:#60a0b0;font-style:italic"># or later to get &amp;#34;unicode_strings&amp;#34; feature, plus strict and warnings&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#007020;font-weight:bold">use&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#0e84b5;font-weight:bold">utf8&lt;/span>; &lt;span style="color:#60a0b0;font-style:italic"># so literals and identifiers can be in UTF-8&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#007020;font-weight:bold">use&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#0e84b5;font-weight:bold">warnings&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#c65d09">qw(FATAL utf8)&lt;/span>; &lt;span style="color:#60a0b0;font-style:italic"># fatalize encoding glitches&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#007020;font-weight:bold">use&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#0e84b5;font-weight:bold">open&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#c65d09">qw(:std :encoding(UTF-8))&lt;/span>; &lt;span style="color:#60a0b0;font-style:italic"># undeclared streams in UTF-8&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#007020;font-weight:bold">use&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#0e84b5;font-weight:bold">Encode&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#c65d09">qw(decode)&lt;/span>;
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#bb60d5">@ARGV&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#666">=&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#007020">map&lt;/span> { decode(&lt;span style="color:#4070a0">&amp;#39;UTF-8&amp;#39;&lt;/span>, &lt;span style="color:#bb60d5">$_&lt;/span>, &lt;span style="color:#0e84b5;font-weight:bold">Encode::&lt;/span>FB_CROAK) } &lt;span style="color:#bb60d5">@ARGV&lt;/span>;
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#60a0b0;font-style:italic">#use autodie qw(:all);&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#60a0b0;font-style:italic">#use Unicode::Normalize; # for NFC(), NFD()&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>say &lt;span style="color:#4070a0">&amp;#34;😊 3 加 4 等于 &amp;#34;&lt;/span>, add(&lt;span style="color:#40a070">3&lt;/span>, &lt;span style="color:#40a070">4&lt;/span>);
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#007020;font-weight:bold">sub&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#06287e">add&lt;/span>($a, $b) {
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#007020;font-weight:bold">return&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#bb60d5">$a&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#666">+&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#bb60d5">$b&lt;/span>;
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>}
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>如果是命令行执行 one-liner 脚本，最好使用如下命令：&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Free Unicode Fonts</title><link>/posts/free-unicode-fonts/</link><pubDate>Thu, 07 Feb 2019 20:18:46 +0800</pubDate><guid>/posts/free-unicode-fonts/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="fonts">Fonts&lt;/h2>
